.js (⭐127k), trpc (⭐36k), Prisma (⭐41k), Vue.js Core (⭐48k), OmniRoute (⭐5.7k). 10+ tahun pengalaman profesional di BITWYRE, GARUDAMEDIA (3000+ karyawan), VIAPULSA. Founder BerkahKarya — 1-Man Company dengan 20+ layanan AI. 8,464 kontribusi di GitHub tahun 2025. Bukan teori doang — praktik beneran dari orang yg kodenya dipake developer di seluruh dunia.</p><div class=\"HeroSection_buttons__AAb79\"><a href=\"/id/belajar/kurikulum\" class=\"HeroSection_primary__XoIi7\">🔴 Ambil Platinum Pass Sekarang →</a><a href=\"#kurikulum\" class=\"HeroSection_secondary__W4nQd\">📚 Lihat Dulu Kurikulumnya</a></div><div class=\"HeroSection_strip__3xnuY\"><div class=\"HeroSection_stripItem___vGpb\"><span>✓</span><span>✅ 150+ GitHub Repos · 8,464 Contributions di 2025</span></div><div class=\"HeroSection_stripItem___vGpb\"><span>✓</span><span>✅ Setup Langsung &lt;5 Menit</span></div><div class=\"HeroSection_stripItem___vGpb\"><span>✓</span><span>✅ Garansi 7 Hari — Gak Cocok? Kembali 100%</span></div></div></div><div class=\"HeroSection_characterWrap__voqYh\"><div class=\"CharacterAvatar_wrapper__0IoSK CharacterAvatar_glow__HUnmw CharacterAvatar_float__W3JJX CharacterAvatar_hero__QGyAr \"><img alt=\"Belajar AI\" fetchpriority=\"high\" width=\"280\" height=\"280\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"CharacterAvatar_image__EmH_M\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fcharacters%2Fvilona-side.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fcharacters%2Fvilona-side.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fcharacters%2Fvilona-side.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section style=\"padding:0 1.5rem 3rem;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center\"><p style=\"font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal-primary);margin-bottom:0.75rem\">Kuasai AI Sekarang — Sebelum Orang Lain Ngambil Posisi Lo.</p><p style=\"font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--text-white-70);line-height:1.7;max-width:650px;margin:0 auto;font-style:italic\">Setiap h